# Animations Directory

This directory contains animated components for the platform:

- **animations/** - Reusable animated React components
  - IsometricHero.tsx - Main landing page hero
  - IsometricCoding.tsx - Coding animation
  - IsometricLearning.tsx - Learning animation
  - FloatingElements.tsx - Floating UI elements
  - CountUp.tsx - Number animations
  - LottiePlayer.tsx - Lottie animation wrapper

Add your animated components here following the naming convention.
